1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 19=

3
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,280
So beautiful.

4
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:17,560
Zhaohua.

5
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,599
Do you know why

6
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:21,719
I gave you this peach tree?

7
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,480
Why?

8
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:24,439
Because I know

9
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:26,079
your childhood name is Yaoyao.

10
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,719
Peach trees in bloom,

11
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:29,000
radiant and bright.

12
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:29,959
I thought

13
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,319
you must love peach trees.

14
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,280
You're so thoughtful.

15
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:38,079
I heard the border battles
have been won recently.

16
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,719
You must be very pleased.

17
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,400
What matters most now

18
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,879
is you

19
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,799
and the health of our child.

20
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,079
Don't trouble yourself

21
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:49,359
with court affairs.

22
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:52,840
I'm not concerned with court affairs.

23
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,799
It's just

24
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:56,000
that I worry
you're overworking yourself.

25
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,719
Oh.

26
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,000
I know

27
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,480
you come from a military family.

28
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,680
You love riding horses

29
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,599
and archery.

30
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,280
Once you've given birth,

31
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,680
I'll take you

32
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,159
to do all the things you love.

33
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:06,879
How about that?

34
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,560
Hearing you say that

35
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,280
makes me so happy.

36
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:12,719
But I wonder

37
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,719
if I'll ever have that chance.

38
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,199
How could you not?

39
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,680
They say a child clings

40
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,039
to their mother in the early years.

41
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:27,560
I'm just worried

42
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,199
I might not have the time.

43
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,400
Alright.

44
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,719
Once you've given birth,

45
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:36,319
the three of us

46
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:38,240
will share a life of joy together.

47
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:02,599
Yukui.

48
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:05,759
Come back with me.

49
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,120
Why are you here?

50
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:08,879
I told you.

51
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,560
We are strangers now.

52
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,680
No more ties.

53
00:03:11,879 --> 00:03:13,439
You say we're strangers, so that's it?

54
00:03:13,759 --> 00:03:14,759
Then what about everything

55
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,520
we went through?

56
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,680
Let go of me.

57
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,439
I won't.

58
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,919
Come back with me first.

59
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:24,039
I'll explain everything once we're back.

60
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,360
I don't want your explanation.

61
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:28,039
I want Zhu Yunqi and Rong Zhaohua dead.

62
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,560
Can you do that?

63
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,719
I don't know why.

64
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,879
But from the day

65
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:36,039
you decided to spare Zhu Yunqi,

66
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,560
I decided to take revenge myself.

67
00:03:39,439 --> 00:03:40,759
If you won't help me,

68
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,960
I have nothing to say.

69
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,840
But if you try to stop me,

70
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:46,599
then from now on, we are enemies.

71
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:47,319
Yukui.

72
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,439
I truly understand

73
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,879
your obsession with revenge.

74
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,319
But have you ever thought

75
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:56,039
what if your revenge is wrong?

76
00:03:59,280 --> 00:03:59,879
Is revenge worth

77
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,919
sacrificing everything you have?

78
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,199
Let it go.

79
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,400
Your vengeance is complete.

80
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,520
You say let it go, just like that?

81
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,960
My vengeance is not complete.

82
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,960
How can I let it go?

83
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,240
His Majesty will be back soon.

84
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,240
Please leave.

85
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,519
I'm not leaving.

86
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:38,800
You're still here?

87
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,560
Jiang Yukui.

88
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:54,720
Your plan worked.

89
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,920
We've had victory after victory
these past few days.

90
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:58,920
I have kept my promise

91
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,319
to you.

92
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,439
Now your promise

93
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:04,160
must also be kept.

94
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,560
Push, Consort Rong!

95
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,839
One more push!

96
00:05:18,959 --> 00:05:20,240
Push, Consort Rong!

97
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,240
Harder!

98
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,040
Consort Rong.

99
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:23,759
Push again.

100
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,480
Push!

101
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,439
Almost there.

102
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:26,240
Almost there!

103
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,480
Why hasn't the baby been born yet?

104
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:38,800
Step back!

105
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,519
Consort Rong.

106
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,879
One more push, Consort Rong!

107
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:47,800
Still delivering?

108
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:49,759
Push!

109
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:50,920
Push!

110
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:52,639
Yes.

111
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,199
It's out!

112
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,160
It's out!

113
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,360
It's out!

114
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,360
Is it a boy or a girl?

115
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,800
A prince!

116
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:16,000
Let me see.

117
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,519
Quick.

118
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,240
Take it away!

119
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:24,560
Where are you taking my child?

120
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,160
My child.

121
00:06:26,079 --> 00:06:26,959
My child.

122
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:28,959
My child!

123
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:39,680
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

124
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,800
It's a prince!

125
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,920
I have a son.

126
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,199
I have a prince!

127
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,639
How is Consort Rong?

128
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:57,639
Reporting, Your Majesty.

129
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:59,360
Everyone else has withdrawn.

130
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,959
Give me back my child!

131
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,199
Jiang Yukui.

132
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,759
Why are you here?

133
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,199
To take your life, of course.

134
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,480
Zhaohua.

135
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,560
(From now on,)

136
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,800
(never appear before me again.)

137
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,720
(I have chosen you.)

138
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:29,360
(I will marry no one else.)

139
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:34,160
(The man I've chosen)

140
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:36,160
(will be the king of this world
one day.)

141
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:51,399
(Rather than be the only one
in your heart,)

142
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:54,160
(I'd rather be the one
you care about most.)

143
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,600
(Am I not?)

144
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,120
Zhaohua.

145
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,759
Zhaohua.

146
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:07,759
Help!

147
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:08,319
Zhaohua.

148
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,000
Save me, Your Majesty!

149
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:15,959
Zhaohua.

150
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:16,519
Your Majesty.

151
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,720
I'm sorry for frightening you.

152
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,959
Zhu Yunqi.

153
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,600
You are the ruler of a nation,

154
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,000
and you go back on your word?

155
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,120
You promised

156
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:28,279
that if the Zhao Tribe defended
your borders,

157
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:30,399
you would give me Rong Zhaohua's life.

158
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,039
Zhaohua.

159
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,440
Wait.

160
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,559
I will explain.

161
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,120
Yes.

162
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,279
I did say that.

163
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:40,799
But now I'm not doing it.

164
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,919
What can you do about it?

165
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:42,879
If you want someone to blame,

166
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:44,039
blame your own stupidity,

167
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,720
thinking you could stand

168
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,799
against me alone.

169
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:47,960
Dream on.

170
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,080
Despicable!

171
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,080
Guards.

172
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,120
Arrest her!

173
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:55,480
Get her!

174
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,000
Go!

175
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:56,360
Yes!

176
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,159
After her!

177
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,320
Search everywhere!

178
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,559
How did you know there'd be trouble?

179
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:20,960
My Lord worried about you.

180
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,639
He had us waiting outside
the city walls.

181
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,480
If you ever encountered danger,

182
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,120
we would know immediately

183
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,960
and protect you.

184
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,240
Have something to eat.

185
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:46,960
You haven't eaten all day.

186
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:51,720
I know you care about me.

187
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,879
But I have no appetite.

188
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,600
You may all leave.

189
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:01,720
Yes.

190
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:12,120
Still thinking about yesterday?

191
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,600
I've been thinking all night.

192
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,759
Everything that happened

193
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,919
is my own fault.

194
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:22,039
You warned me before

195
00:10:22,399 --> 00:10:23,679
that I couldn't stand

196
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,279
against

197
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:27,000
Zhu Yunqi and Rong Zhaohua alone.

198
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:30,679
I should have trusted you.

199
00:10:31,279 --> 00:10:33,639
I ruined my own chance at revenge.

200
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,120
Yukui.

201
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:38,000
Have you ever thought

202
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,039
about leaving all this behind

203
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:41,360
and going somewhere else with me?

204
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,279
The world outside has mountains,
lakes, and seas.

205
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:46,440
There are so many beautiful places.

206
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:50,780
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

207
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,399
I've been caged since birth.

208
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,200
All those things you speak of,

209
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,159
I don't know them.

210
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,639
I do, and that's enough.

211
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,799
With me,

212
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,120
you'll come to know them too.

213
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,639
If you're willing,

214
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:07,399
I can take you to my hometown first.

215
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,480
The lake there is emerald green,

216
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,799
the distant mountains dark as ink.

217
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,399
Can I go just because I want to?

218
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,679
You are Lord Nine-Thousand.

219
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:20,039
Can you really just leave?

220
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:21,960
Leave it all to me.

221
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:26,940
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

222
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:30,500
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

223
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:33,740
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

224
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:37,180
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪

225
00:11:42,279 --> 00:11:43,440
You're really leaving?

226
00:11:45,759 --> 00:11:46,679
You're leaving

227
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:49,080
for that woman, aren't you?

228
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,720
I believe this is the best choice.

229
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:53,720
Fine.

230
00:11:54,759 --> 00:11:55,679
I'll grant your wish.

231
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:00,960
With this decree,

232
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,679
you may enter and leave Kun freely.

233
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:03,840
I hope

234
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:05,720
you will return one day.

235
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,759
Remember this.

236
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,679
If you continue to rule

237
00:12:18,679 --> 00:12:20,440
with the same cruelty as before,

238
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,399
I will come back and bring you
to justice.

239
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,519
Wait.

240
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,000
I promise you.

241
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,120
I will be a wise ruler.

242
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:01,220
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

243
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:03,140
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

244
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:06,460
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

245
00:13:06,780 --> 00:13:10,580
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

246
00:13:13,540 --> 00:13:15,260
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

247
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:16,780
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

248
00:13:17,140 --> 00:13:20,540
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

249
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:24,540
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

250
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:28,860
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

251
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:32,420
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

252
00:13:32,420 --> 00:13:34,740
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

253
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:38,940
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

254
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:41,020
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

255
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:42,540
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

256
00:13:42,540 --> 00:13:45,740
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

257
00:13:46,140 --> 00:13:48,060
♪In dreams, it's you♪

258
00:13:48,060 --> 00:13:49,460
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

259
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:52,780
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

260
00:13:52,780 --> 00:13:56,180
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

261
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:59,740
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

262
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:02,980
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

263
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:06,420
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
